&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-3534&quot; title=&quot;LevelRangeFilterBuilder loses compatibility with log4j1.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LOG4J2-3534&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LOG4J2-3534&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Fix LevelRangeFilterBuilder to align with log4j1&apos;s behavior (#924)&lt;/p&gt;

